                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17891028-13-off63 t17891028-13-cd64"></join>, three ounces of hair, value 2 s. two razors, value 1 s. two brushes, value 2 d. a card with iron teeth, value 1 s. a pair of scissars, value 2 d. a pewter bason, value 6 d. one puff, value 6 d. one silk ditto, value 3 d. two horn combs, value 3 d. one linen dressing cloth, value 6 d. one towel, value 6 d. one pair of curling irons, value 2 d. a hatchet, value 2 d. a curtain, value 6 d. a powder knife, value 2 d. two prints with wooden frames, value 6 d. and two pair of fire tongs, value 1 s.
